HEADWORD: Breadless
<hw>Bread"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without bread; destitute of
food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Plump peers and <qex>breadless</qex> bards alike are dull.</q>
<rj><qau>P. Whitehead.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

